Early Christmas with MT Group🥰🎄 Blessed to be a blessing!✨

Gabisa flexing “Daddy i punya ini, Daddy i punya itu”, but I am proudly sure that I have the sweetest Daddy and that is more than enough!🥰💫
.
After losing certain people in my life, now I learned kalau kita gabisa percaya sepenuhnya sama orang lain. Karena kita gapernah tau isi hati orang dan bisa aja orang gasuka sama kita (even sahabat sendiri atau orang yang kita deket). At the end, you only have your family, cause the right parents pasti cuma mau yang terbaik buat anaknya (walaupun caranya berbeda-beda).
.
And I am blessed to have this amazing Dad in my life!❤️ Thank you for showing me what true love feels like. Dari semua kekecewaan dan kegagalan yang dialamin, you keep telling to always be kind, take it easy, and choose happiness over sorrows. Bersyukurr banget bisa punya papi yang terbuka, Bella bisa cerita apapun setiap saat, sangat open minded tapi wise + tetep asiikkkk brooo!🤘(Tapi mami Bella lebih hebat lagi @dewisusianti88 😘).
.
Thankful for the endless love and support from you, so that I can make it until today! You’re my best friend, brother, mentor, and best dad since day 1!🏆❤️‍🔥

Finally, I learned to forgive and let go🤍 2023 has too many plot twists in my life. All the disappointments were haunting me along the year. I had no trust in any person anymore, I tried not to be attached with anyone, and I pushed away people to protect my own self.
.
This year, I moved to a new place to have my own time and to have my own life alone. I do enjoy it, I look happy all the time. But deep inside, I keep holding the pain and anger. 
.
And finally I realized, I just need to forgive and let go. It ain’t easy AT ALL. I keep telling myself “YOUR SOUL DESERVES PEACE. I release from within me all the bitterness and resentment little by little. I gently let go of old hurts and forgive everyone, including myself.”
.
Exhale the negativity, inhale the positivity. When you forgive, you heal. And when you let go, you grow✨
.
*Melukat is just a Bali’s ritual to clean and purify our body, mind, and soul. You can’t just forgive and let go things by doing rituals, you gotta do it everyday until you’re full healed by your own🫶
